"Set or remove the completer function.  If *function* is specified, it will "
"be used as the new completer function; if omitted or ``None``, any completer "
"function already installed is removed.  The completer function is called as "
"``function(text, state)``, for *state* in ``0``, ``1``, ``2``, ..., until it "
"returns a non-string value.  It should return the next possible completion "
"starting with *text*."
msgstr ""
"Define ou remove a funĂ§Ă£o de autocomplemento. Se *function* for "
"especificada, ela serĂ¡ usada como a nova funĂ§Ă£o de autocomplemento; se "
"omitido ou ``None``, qualquer funĂ§Ă£o de autocomplemento jĂ¡ instalada serĂ¡ "
"removida. A funĂ§Ă£o de autocomplemento Ă© chamada como ``function(text, "
"state)``, para *state* em ``0``, ``1``, ``2``, ..., atĂ© retornar um valor "
"que nĂ£o seja string. Deve retornar o prĂ³ximo autocomplemento possĂ­vel "
"comeĂ§ando com *text*."

#: ../../library/readline.rst:269
msgid ""
"The installed completer function is invoked by the *entry_func* callback "
