"ObtĂ©m a funĂ§Ă£o de autocomplemento ou ``None`` se nenhuma funĂ§Ă£o de "
"autocomplemento tiver sido definida."

#: ../../library/readline.rst:283
msgid ""
"Get the type of completion being attempted.  This returns the :c:data:`!"
